  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Rabbit Antithymocyte Globulin 3mg/kg in Kidney Transplant Patients Under Steroid-free and CNI Minimization Maintenance Immunosuppressive Regimen</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Rabbit Antithymocyte Globulin 3mg/kg vs. 6mg/kg in Kidney Transplant Patients Under Steroid-free and CNI Minimization Maintenance Immunosuppressive Regimen</official_title>
