  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Single-center, prospective, randomized, open-label clinical trial to evaluate the 1-year
      efficacy and safety of rATG 3mg/kg compared to 6mg/kg in low to moderate immunological risk
      patients receiving low exposure tacrolimus plus everolimus (EVL) in a steroid-free protocol.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
